## 2. Subscription Services

### 2.1 Premium Subscription Options
Yada offers auto-renewable subscriptions and one-time purchases:

- **Premium Yearly Subscription**: $4.99/year (USD)
  - Billed annually
  - Auto-renews unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period
  - Family Sharing eligible

- **Lifetime Premium**: $8.99 (USD)
  - One-time purchase
  - Unlimited access forever
  - Family Sharing eligible

### 2.2 Subscription Features
Premium subscription includes:
- Unlimited daily questions
- Access to all premium themes
- Custom theme creation
- Future premium features

### 2.3 Free Trial
New users may be offered a free trial period. If you don't cancel before the trial ends, you will be charged the subscription price.

## 3. Payment Terms

### 3.1 Billing
